Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}---Text---
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.78,0:00:01.85,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}爱 那必须是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:04.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要比什么都更尊贵 更美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:09.22,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有更勤勉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:12.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是向所爱之人传达心情的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:13.99,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:17.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:51.45,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:52.93,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:55.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要把巧克力交给喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.12,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这好像是和真的世界里的一种习俗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:01.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我最喜欢巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:04.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但竟然要分给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像有点浪费啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}惠惠要给谁巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.61,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竟 竟然秒答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为他看起来就跟和情人节无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算说只有从妈妈那边拿到过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也一点都不会惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:22.38,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}顺带一提
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.27,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}爱蜜莉雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有想送的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:26.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帕克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:30.06,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}耶 那我也给莉雅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.25,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你啰 帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.83,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那应该不是这样的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:37.03,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}少校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.33,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家都聚在这做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:44.54,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家正在讨论情人节的事情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:46.75,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.97,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是那个用宗教的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}配合资本主义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.34,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}获得市场胜利的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.54,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好厉害的解释啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:58.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}少校有打算给谁巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然以我个人而言是完全没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.60,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但以税制上的经费观点来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:07.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}作为交际费来支出一些也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.46,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是所谓的义理巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.99,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}义理巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.47,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊 就是和友人或职场相关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}表达"接下来也请多多指教"的东西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以要发很多巧克力出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.18,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}便宜小小的那种就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}聊表心意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么 也要给昴这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.05,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所谓的义理巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是个好主意呢 莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.27,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}昴也真辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}情人节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}终于到了这个我唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:45.82,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}对愚蠢的人类给予正面评价的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这个甜美的漆黑之物中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}倾注我的爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.27,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把爱把爱把爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给灌注到巧克力里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.46,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 贝特鲁吉乌斯老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.10,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}回答的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:03.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我正是勤勉的爱的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:07.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}贝特鲁吉乌斯·罗曼尼康帝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.72,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽说是巧克力但可是有很多种类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你 希望做的是哪一种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为安兹大人是所有亡灵的统治者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:23.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要选一个最适合黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:25.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}漆黑的苦甜巧克力才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.93,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不是甜味 而是大人的苦味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用我溢出的爱来装饰巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.84,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}然后隐藏的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还是我的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太棒了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}竟然能在这种地方遇见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如此勤勉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.79,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在爱安兹大人这点上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.11,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是一点都不容许怠惰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.18,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正是正是正是正是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:51.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你正是勤勉的爱的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 我就是安兹大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}爱的奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:04:59.54,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:00.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和真他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.53,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}下定了决心 绝对不会靠近这群人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们两个人要给谁巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.15,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}安兹大人啰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷姆的会给昴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}达克妮丝不会给和真吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.05,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}给和 和真吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和真只是单纯的伙伴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.82,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.59,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}明明是和他比剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却用魔法把我弄得一身湿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让父亲看到我乱七八糟的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.10,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还边把我得体力夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}边舔着舌头说着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.07,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}"我要对你做不得了的事情"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样的男人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那 那对你而言应该是奖赏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个世界的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.31,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的是太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.74,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让我几乎都快忘了我在之前的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.16,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吃过的巧克力的味道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:52.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且今天不是一年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:58.15,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}由女性配给巧克力给我们的日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:58.87,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我真的可以享受这么幸福的节日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.90,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天并不是那样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:07.75,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天是女性会把巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.76,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}送给有好感的对象的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能收到有着浓浓心意的巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那不是太棒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.22,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个人没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他还是没搞懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:19.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.78,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吧你个头啦 诺伊曼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.96,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你也稍微跟这个脑内的花田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正绽放着的家伙解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.29,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.04,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.54,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 就如太尉所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:35.68,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天是可以和女性索取巧克力的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:39.94,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是收的时候必须要有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:43.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有礼貌吗 那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喂 和真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是诺伊曼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:48.61,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:51.10,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想要从对方那里拿到巧克力的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在你的世界会怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:07:00.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}应该是"Give me chocolate"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.29,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}"Give me chocolate"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像这样伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.16,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}恭敬地低下头多说几次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:12.34,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}巧克力一定可以爱拿多少就拿多少啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}感谢你 和真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没什么 不用跟我客气喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:17.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.40,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么想都是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吧你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉这不是当真了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.91,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}夏提雅她们往这边走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.32,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Give me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.05,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Choco…late!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你 你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Give me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.51,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Choco…late!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.09,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等等 你这个大浓眉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.26,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要袭击的话就冲着我来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.67,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Give me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:59.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Choco…late!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.49,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}埃尔修玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.76,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.12,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家都不给我巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.02,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.13,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吧你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.50,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉也太可怜了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.62,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全身破破烂烂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.58,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}少校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:29.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.69,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Give
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:34.98,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.66,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Give me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.89,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜斯太尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.65,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.73,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你被骗了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.23,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.70,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的真的真的太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:59.26,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这正是爱的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:02.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们在 做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.56,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我正在为我所爱的安兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.46,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亲手做巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.81,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}勤勉的 没错 勤勉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:13.64,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那的确是非常好的事情没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.82,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那 这边这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.30,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:20.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我是勤勉的爱的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.23,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}担任"怠惰"的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.42,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}贝特鲁吉乌斯·罗曼尼康帝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:28.01,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是非法入侵喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.43,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.80,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}毕竟我已经完成我的目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:45.08,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}唉呀 我感觉到那边也有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是爱 爱的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不快去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.03,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢您 爱的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:55.63,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这不是雅儿贝德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:57.35,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你一个人在这里做巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.55,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是昴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}话说你觉得看起来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:04.24,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}安兹大人会喜欢这个情人节巧克力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.27,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:08.14,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.37,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不觉得充满了 充满了爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.52,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:16.21,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我对这个设计充满了负面观感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}确实好像蕴含着很强烈的爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:50.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可是 我不能吃巧克力啊
